comments: Poole (GSW) momentarily places his of hand on the upper body of Hayes (NOP), but does not push off to dislodge him from his guarding position. Hayes' (NOP) momentum is carrying him in the direction of the basket.
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Marshall (NOP) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Poole (GSW) cleanly dislodges the ball from Alexander-Walker (NOP) during his driving shot attempt.
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) legally takes two steps on his way to the basket and does not hop consecutively on the same foot upon gathering the ball.
Hayes (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Mulder (GSW) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Mannion (GSW) legally contests Marshall's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
Bell (GSW) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting the driving shot attempt by Alexander-Walker (NOP).
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) legally contests Alexander-Walker's (NOP) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Hayes (NOP) commits a take foul on Paschall (GSW).
Lewis Jr. (NOP) commits a take foul on Poole (GSW).
